snippet.description:

▼ EXPAND ME ▼

This is Genshin Impact 2.3 event - Shadow Amidst Snowstorms.

While Paimon asks Timaeus and Sucrose to make her weird stuff, they realized something off from Albedo. They decided to go to Dragonspine. At the entrance, they met Amber and Cyrus. They also asked Joel to join them. While at it, Eula also was asked by Amber to join their adventure. At the dragonspine, something seemed very off, especially when they met Albedo. I'm not spoiling any further, enjoy the video!

Thank you for watching!
